Ivory Coast: the list of Kamara, without Cornet (OL)
Ibrahima Kamara has unveiled her list for the CAN 2021 qualifiers, without Lyonnais Maxwel Cornet in particular.
06 Nov 2019, 12:21 by Thomas Rassouli


CAN 2019: CÃ´te d'Ivoire's video tour




Ivory Coast is entering a new phase of the playoffs of the next African Cup of Nations. On 16 and 19 November, the Elephants will face Niger and Ethiopia for two confrontations at stake.
